org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.partition.spec

Class PartitionSpecWithSharedSDProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.partition.spec.PartitionSpecProxy
      • org.apache.hadoop.hive.metastore.partition.spec.PartitionSpecWithSharedSDProxy

  • public class PartitionSpecWithSharedSDProxy
extends PartitionSpecProxy
    Subclass of PartitionSpecProxy that pulls out commonality of StorageDescriptor properties within a Partition-list into a common StorageDescriptor instance.
